race.comment: The scratchings have decimated this race in terms of the leading chances. That gives BRUTIFY (9) a live chance to break through and now break from a much better gate. Hasn't been far away in two runs form a break, finishing sixth both times, when coming from well back. Fitter and will be tough to hold out. BRAZEN FLING (8) is overdue having placed at all three this time in, the latest making good ground to run third. Another bold showing is expected.  GOOD BOY CARLO (2) placed fresh then was disappointing last time. Fitter again  and has paced 4/5 this journey. Has ability and gets chance to bounce back.  LONHRO'S SHADOW (14) comes right into it now. Was safely held at only run then spelled again. Jumping out well and returns with the blinkers added. Worth another chance,
